            "itemType": "journalArticle",
            "title": "On the phylogeny of Miniopterus schreibersii schreibersii and Miniopterus schreibersii pallidus from Asia Minor in reference to other Miniopterus taxa (Chiroptera: Vespertilionidae)",
            "creators": [
                {
