            "title": "Mitochondrial DNA confirms low genetic variation of the greater mouse-eared bats, Myotis myotis, in Central Europe",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Josef",
                    "lastName": "Bryja"
