            "title": "Skull Morphology of Two Cryptic Bat Species: Pipistrellus pipistrellus and P. pygmaeus — A 3D Geometric Morphometrics Approach with Landmark Reconstruction",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Anna",
                    "lastName": "Sztencel-Jabłonka"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
