            "title": "Phylogeography of the greater horseshoe bat, Rhinolophus ferrumequinum (Chiroptera: Rhinolophidae), in southeastern Europe and Anatolia, with a specific focus on whether the Sea of Marmara is a barrier to gene flow",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Raşit",
                    "lastName": "Bilgin"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Emrah",
